WILL, Appellant, v. BARNWELL, Respondent. (Supreme Court, . Appellate Division, Fourth Department. March 19, 1909.)

Action by John Will against Chas. P. Barnwell. No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to Court of Appeals denied, with $10 costs. See, also, 60 Misc. Rep. 458, 112 N. Y. Supp. 462.
